<h2 id=3D"PRDTPL-Background">Background</h2>
<p>To continue to provide more services to our customers, we will contact o=
ther warehouses and deploy WMS Software in 3rd party warehouse. in this way=
, it will increase the warehouse number and can do more distribution for ou=
r customers and help them to save shipping fees.</p>
